Package: syntheticdata
Title: Synthetic Clinical Data Generation and Privacy-Preserving Validation
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Cuiwei", "Gao", , "48gaocuiwei@gmail.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"))
Description: Generates synthetic clinical datasets that preserve
    statistical properties while protecting patient privacy. Implements
    parametric resampling, conditional distribution modeling, and noise
    injection methods with built-in utility and privacy metrics.
    Designed for GDPR and HIPAA compliant data sharing in multi-site
    clinical research. Validates synthetic data quality via distributional
    similarity, discriminative accuracy, and downstream model fidelity.
    Methods described in Jordon et al. (2022)
    <doi:10.1038/s42256-022-00534-z>.
